@startuml Deployment Architecture
title County Connect Deployment Architecture

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam componentStyle uml2

' Client Layer
package "Client Layer" as Client #LightBlue {
    [Web Browser] as Browser
    note right : Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge\nResponsive design\nProgressive Web App ready
}

' Web Server Layer
package "Web Server Layer" as WebServer #LightGreen {
    [Apache HTTP Server] as Apache
    note right : Port 80/443 (HTTP/HTTPS)\nServes static React files\nReverse proxy for API\nSSL/TLS termination
}

' Application Server Layer
package "Application Server Layer" as AppServer #LightYellow {
    [PHP-FPM Process Manager] as PHPFPM
    [API Application] as APIApp
    note right : PHP 8.1+ runtime\nFastCGI Process Manager\nAPI request processing\nSession management
}

' Database Server Layer
package "Database Server Layer" as DBServer #LightOrange {
    [MySQL Database Server] as MySQL
    [Database Files] as DBFiles
    note right : Port 3306\nInnoDB storage engine\nConnection pooling\nBackup & replication ready
}

' File Storage Layer
package "File Storage Layer" as FileStorage #LightGray {
    [Local File System] as LocalFS
    [Report Files] as Reports
    [Upload Files] as Uploads
    note right : Document storage\nReport generation output\nUser uploaded files\nAccess controlled
}

' External Services
package "External Services" as External #Pink {
    [Email Service] as Email
    [SMS Gateway] as SMS
    [Government APIs] as GovAPI
    note right : SMTP for notifications\nSMS for alerts\nExternal data integration
}

' Network connections
Browser --> Apache : HTTPS (443)\nStatic files + API calls
Apache --> PHPFPM : FastCGI\nAPI requests
PHPFPM --> MySQL : MySQL Protocol (3306)\nDatabase queries
PHPFPM --> LocalFS : File I/O\nRead/write files
PHPFPM --> Email : SMTP (587)\nSend emails
PHPFPM --> SMS : HTTPS\nSend SMS
PHPFPM --> GovAPI : HTTPS\nExternal data

' Data flow labels
Browser ..> Apache : "GET /index.html\nPOST /api/auth/login"
Apache ..> PHPFPM : "API request routing"
PHPFPM ..> MySQL : "SELECT * FROM users\nINSERT INTO citizens"
PHPFPM ..> LocalFS : "Store report.pdf\nRead config.json"

' Deployment environment
package "Development Environment" as Dev #LightCyan {
    component [Localhost] as LocalDev
    note right : XAMPP/WAMP/MAMP\nHot reload development\nDebug logging enabled\nLocal database
}

package "Production Environment" as Prod #LightRed {
    component [Cloud Server] as CloudProd
    note right : VPS/Cloud instance\nLoad balancer ready\nSSL certificates\nMonitoring & logging
}

' Development connections
LocalDev --> Apache : Development server
LocalDev --> MySQL : Local database
LocalDev --> LocalFS : Local file storage

' Production connections
CloudProd --> Apache : Production server
CloudProd --> MySQL : Production database
CloudProd --> LocalFS : Production storage

' Configuration notes
note as Config
**Server Configuration:**
Apache: mod_rewrite, mod_ssl, mod_php
PHP: php.ini optimized, extensions loaded
MySQL: max_connections=100, innodb_buffer_pool_size
Security: Firewall rules, SSL certificates, CORS policy
end note

' Performance notes
note as Performance
**Performance Considerations:**
- Apache caching headers
- PHP opcode caching (OPcache)
- MySQL query optimization
- File system permissions
- CDN ready for static assets
end note

' Monitoring notes
note as Monitoring
**Monitoring & Logging:**
- Apache access/error logs
- PHP error logging
- MySQL slow query log
- Application audit trails
- Health check endpoints
end note
@enduml